1220
01:22:44,125 --> 01:22:46,491
And then she called us,
and then you were fucked.

1221
01:22:46,561 --> 01:22:48,688
The case is closed, Patrick.
The case is closed.

1222
01:22:48,763 --> 01:22:51,061
Coke-dealing Haitian's
a pretty easy target for a frame.

1223
01:22:51,132 --> 01:22:52,429
- Lionel?
- Excuse me.

1224
01:22:52,500 --> 01:22:53,558
- Look at me.
- Okay. Excuse me.

1225
01:22:53,635 --> 01:22:55,262
You took your niece,
