1257
01:25:11,940 --> 01:25:14,500
<i>Started calling the papers.
Hired you.</i>

1258
01:25:14,576 --> 01:25:16,908
Lionel don't want me coming here,
now you don't want the job?

1259
01:25:16,978 --> 01:25:20,971
But once you found the money,
they had Amanda and the money.

1260
01:25:21,049 --> 01:25:25,179
So they decided to set up
a fake exchange for you to witness.

1261
01:25:25,253 --> 01:25:27,915
<i>They got Chris Mullen
to set up Cheese at the quarry.</i>

1262
01:25:27,989 --> 01:25:31,584
15K and a chance to be the boss.

1263
01:25:34,395 --> 01:25:36,693
<i>Cheese figured out what was happening.</i>

1264
01:25:36,764 --> 01:25:40,222
<i>Even though it was too late,
