1265
01:25:40,301 --> 01:25:42,235
<i>Panicking.</i>

1266
01:25:44,873 --> 01:25:47,205
<i>And she just fell.
I mean, she just...</i>

1267
01:25:47,275 --> 01:25:48,936
She fell in.

1268
01:25:50,411 --> 01:25:52,038
She's gone.

1269
01:25:52,113 --> 01:25:54,308
It was an accident.
It was just an accident.

1270
01:25:54,382 --> 01:25:56,577
She was your sister's kid, Lionel.

1271
01:25:58,486 --> 01:26:02,149
- Your sister's child.
