On the floor. On the floor!

1288
01:27:08,656 --> 01:27:10,317
- Hands on your head. Do it.
- Oh, my God.

1289
01:27:10,391 --> 01:27:11,983
Everybody stays calm,
this'll be over in a minute.

1290
01:27:12,060 --> 01:27:14,995
Hey, do you know
whose bar this is, shithead?

1291
01:27:15,563 --> 01:27:18,430
Or you can get wise,
it's up to you.

1292
01:27:21,169 --> 01:27:22,966
