1303
01:27:44,325 --> 01:27:47,055
Oh, fuck, God. Amanda McCready
was taken by Remy Bressant!

1304
01:27:47,128 --> 01:27:48,959
- Wait. Wait. Jesus.
- Remy Bressant.

1305
01:27:49,030 --> 01:27:50,588
God damn it. Remy Bressant!

1306
01:27:50,665 --> 01:27:51,723
Amanda McCready was taken

1307
01:27:51,799 --> 01:27:52,925
- by Remy Bressant.
- Jesus. I told him.

1308
01:27:53,001 --> 01:27:55,492
I told him we took her for ransom.
I told him. I told him, Remy.

1309
01:27:55,570 --> 01:27:59,006
Please, I told him we took her for ransom.
I did it.

1310
01:27:59,073 --> 01:28:00,938
Remy, please.

1311
01:28:01,175 --> 01:28:02,642
Please.

1312
01:28:20,928 --> 01:28:22,793
Are you all right?

1313
01:28:23,965 --> 01:28:24,989
Stay with him.

1314
01:29:27,362 --> 01:29:29,125
Drop your gun.

1315
01:29:30,865 --> 01:29:32,560
Put it down!

1316
01:29:37,305 --> 01:29:40,797
That bartender wasn't fucking around.

1317
01:29:50,451 --> 01:29:51,975
What did you do?

1318
01:29:52,854 --> 01:29:54,344
Did you get her killed?

1319
01:29:57,225 --> 01:29:58,920
Say yes.

1320
01:30:03,898 --> 01:30:05,229
Say yes.

1321
01:30:06,167 --> 01:30:07,634
Say yes!

1322
01:30:08,536 --> 01:30:12,700
What're you gonna do? Shoot me?
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

1323
01:30:27,054 --> 01:30:29,079
She was a child.

1324
01:30:31,225 --> 01:30:33,125
I love children.

1325
01:31:09,964 --> 01:31:13,559
Why would I expose a conspiracy
that I was a part of?

1326
01:31:14,969 --> 01:31:18,496
I mean, did Lionel contradict
anything I've said?

1327
01:31:19,740 --> 01:31:22,971
Did any of the witnesses at the bar
contradict anything I've said?

1328
01:31:23,044 --> 01:31:26,707
A police officer was killed today.
That's not looked on lightly.

1329
01:31:26,781 --> 01:31:28,976
Is corruption looked on lightly?

1330
01:31:29,050 --> 01:31:30,711
Is a little girl getting killed
looked on lightly?

1331
01:31:30,785 --> 01:31:32,013
Whoa, hold on.

1332
01:31:32,086 --> 01:31:34,520
