1357
01:33:01,375 --> 01:33:02,569
<i>You think I don't miss her.</i>

1358
01:33:02,643 --> 01:33:05,077
She was more my kid than Helene's.

1359
01:33:05,146 --> 01:33:07,273
I love children.

1360
01:33:11,786 --> 01:33:16,018
This is the kind of thing that if you do,
Patrick, you wanna be sure.

1361
01:33:18,292 --> 01:33:20,021
Are you sure?

1362
01:33:20,728 --> 01:33:22,127
No.

1363
01:33:25,967 --> 01:33:27,832
Are you coming?

1364
01:33:28,469 --> 01:33:29,766
No.

1365
01:33:41,415 --> 01:33:44,145
<i>Doyle brought Remy from Louisiana
back in '72.</i>

1366
01:33:44,218 --> 01:33:46,914
<i>Care to read the highlighted portion?</i>

1367
01:33:58,599 --> 01:34:00,931
Taking a trip?

1368
01:34:01,002 --> 01:34:02,765
Patrick Kenzie.

1369
01:34:04,372 --> 01:34:07,170
