1370
01:34:07,241 --> 01:34:09,869
Remy Bressant died last night.

1371
01:34:10,411 --> 01:34:13,437
I was told. It's a shame.

1372
01:34:14,882 --> 01:34:19,478
Yeah, it's hard to understand.
Because he seemed like a good man.

1373
01:34:19,553 --> 01:34:21,384
He was a good man.

1374
01:34:22,723 --> 01:34:25,385
We don't know why people do
what they do.

1375
01:34:25,726 --> 01:34:28,058
Everybody looks out his own window.

1376
01:34:28,295 --> 01:34:30,456
And everyone's got their reasons.

1377
01:34:40,875 --> 01:34:42,570
- Hey.
- Hi.

1378
01:34:42,643 --> 01:34:43,940
- How are you?
- Good.

1379
01:34:44,011 --> 01:34:46,070
<i>Nick! They're firing at me.</i>

1380
01:34:46,147 --> 01:34:47,842
