1381
01:34:47,915 --> 01:34:49,075
Remy!

1382
01:34:49,150 --> 01:34:51,414
- I heard something go in the water!
- Ambush! Ambush!

1383
01:34:51,485 --> 01:34:54,386
- Something went in!
- Run. Remy. Run!

1384
01:34:55,156 --> 01:34:56,453
<i>Panicking.</i>

1385
01:34:56,524 --> 01:34:59,357
<i>Amanda got scared.
She started running.</i>

1386
01:34:59,427 --> 01:35:02,362
<i>She just fell.
