1400
01:35:28,189 --> 01:35:30,316
Please, I told him we took her
for ransom. I did it.

1401
01:35:30,391 --> 01:35:32,450
I told him. Remy, please.

1402
01:35:37,598 --> 01:35:38,860
So now you know.

1403
01:35:39,734 --> 01:35:42,225
<i>My sister's not stable.
