1412
01:36:03,991 --> 01:36:06,983
<i>Do one last good thing
before we hang it up.</i>

1413
01:36:08,763 --> 01:36:11,823
<i>How many children
have we seen destroyed?</i>

1414
01:36:12,800 --> 01:36:14,097
